Package com.thomsonreuters.upa.ansipage

This package contains classes and interfaces for encoding and decoding ANSI page data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CellColor
    The CellColor enumeration is used to define the foreground and background colors for each PageCell object.
    CellStyle
    The CellStyle enumeration is used to define the style of each PageCell object.
    GraphicSet
    The GraphicSet enumeration is used to define the graphic set that will be associated with each PageCell object.
    Page
    The Page interface is the heart of the AnsiPage API.
    PageCell
    PageCell is used to create the building blocks that make up an ANSI Page.
    PageUpdate
    The PageUpdate interface provide the ability to track updates that are made to the PageCell of an ANSI page.

Package com.thomsonreuters.upa.ansipage Description

This package contains classes and interfaces for encoding and decoding ANSI page data.
